---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Fabrizio Guccione" description="Creative technologist at NYU ITP building at the intersection of AI, hardware, and interactive art.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold gradient-text mb-8">about me</h1>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-purple-200 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        I'm <strong class="text-purple-100">Fabrizio Guccione</strong>, a creative technologist at
        <a href="https://itp.nyu.edu" target="_blank" class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300 underline decoration-purple-500/30 underline-offset-2">NYU's Interactive Telecommunications Program (ITP)</a>.
        I build things at the intersection of AI, physical computing, and interactive experiences.
      </p>

      <p>
        My work tends to live in the space between disciplines that don't usually talk to each other.
        I've built a pipeline that turns spoken descriptions of clothes into 3D models, an autonomous
        AI agent you control by speaking wishes into a camera, and interactive installations with
        thermal printers and Arduino.
      </p>

      <p>
        I believe the most interesting technology is the kind that surprises you — the kind where
        your first reaction is "wait, that shouldn't be possible yet." That's what I try to make.
      </p>

      <div class="card mt-10">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-100 mb-4">what i work with</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-purple-400 font-medium mb-2">AI / ML</h3>
            <p class="text-purple-300">Stable Diffusion, CLIP, Whisper, TensorFlow, LLaVA, Claude, computer vision, body pose estimation</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-purple-400 font-medium mb-2">Hardware</h3>
            <p class="text-purple-300">Arduino, OAK-D cameras, thermal printers, 3D printing, physical computing</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-purple-400 font-medium mb-2">Creative Coding</h3>
            <p class="text-purple-300">p5.js, ml5.js, Processing, generative art, interactive installations</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-purple-400 font-medium mb-2">Web</h3>
            <p class="text-purple-300">TypeScript, Svelte, React, Astro, Node.js, Cloudflare Workers</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 flex gap-4 flex-wrap">
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/fabriziog/" target="_blank" class="badge hover:bg-purple-600/30 transition-colors">linkedin</a>
        <a href="https://x.com/fabricated_it" target="_blank" class="badge hover:bg-purple-600/30 transition-colors">x / twitter</a>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/fabricated.it/" target="_blank" class="badge hover:bg-purple-600/30 transition-colors">instagram</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/FabriGu" target="_blank" class="badge hover:bg-purple-600/30 transition-colors">github</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
